item.description:
Join Successful Anonymous Networking as we meet in Newton on November 2nd! With the holidays fast approaching, many folks tend to feel stress not only on their time and their finances, but also on their waistlines! This meeting will feature time for open networking, light hors d'oeveurs, and brief talking points from 3 keynote speakers.

 

Speakers include -

Marie Wetmore

Life & Career Coach

Lions Share Coaching

 

Dr. Rob Mirandola

Chiropractor

Allasso Chiropractic

 

Dimitry Neyshtadt

Financial Consultant

Wellesley Financial Group
